\v 8 看​哪​，​我​要​使​<a name="02303800800022" ll="SDBH:אָחָז:000000" tl="HOTTP3127">亞哈斯</a>​日晷​上​隨​<a name="02303800800028" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Sun;Sun_pillar;Sunrise;Sunset;Sunset_on_mountain" tl="HOTTP3128">太陽</a>​<a name="02303800800016" ll="SDBH:ירד:000000">前進</a>​的​<a name="02303800800008" ll="SDBH:צֵל:000000">影子</a>​，​<a name="02303800800030" ll="SDBH:אֲחֹרַנִּית:000000">往後</a>​<a name="02303800800004" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">退</a>​<a name="02303800800032" ll="SDBH:עֶשֶׂר:000000">十</a>​<a name="02303800800034" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָה:000002">度</a>​。​」​於是​，​在​日晷​上​<a name="02303800800056" ll="SDBH:ירד:000000">照</a>​<a name="02303800800056" ll="SDBH:ירד:000000">下來</a>​的​<a name="02303800800042" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000">日影</a>​果然​往後​<a name="02303800800038" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000022">退</a>​了​<a name="02303800800044" ll="SDBH:עֶשֶׂר:000000">十</a>​<a name="02303800800046" ll="SDBH:מַעֲלָה:000002">度</a>​。
    
\v 9 
